title: BRIEF-Paynova proposes rights issue of SEK 21 million
text:
BRIEF-Paynova proposes rights issue of SEK 21 million Sept 18 
* Proposes to carry out rights issue of 21 million Swedish crowns ($2.57 million) 
* Subscription price is 0.40 crown per share
